official_title: A bill to designate certain lands in the Cleveland National Forest, California, as the Agua Tibia Wilderness for inclusion in the National Wilderness Preservation System.

summary.text: Designates specified lands in the Cleveland National Forest, California, as the "Agua Tibia Wilderness" for inclusion in the National Wilderness Preservation System.
